Adcock Seeks Government Clarity on AIDS Drug Tender, Business Report Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-03-29T05:20:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/adcock-seeks-government-clarity-on-aids-drug-tender-business-report-says.html
Adcock Ingram Holdings Ltd. (AIP)  wants
to meet with  South Africa ’s National Treasury about concerns it
raised over the outcome of a contract to supply anti-AIDS drugs,
 Business Report  said, citing Jonathan Louw, the chief executive
officer.  The company asked the Treasury for information on the
tender, including the application of the criteria used to assess
the offers, the Johannesburg-based newspaper cited Louw as
saying. Adcock’s rival won a bigger portion of the contract
awarded last year, it said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
